Shrink listings map vertically; especially on mobile

The 560px-tall map dominated the viewport on phones (typical ~700px tall),
pushing the list of rentals well below the fold. Step the map height
responsively so the list is reachable without scrolling past a giant map:

  mobile  : 300px (~40% of a typical phone viewport)
  sm 640+ : 400px
  lg 1024+: 520px

MapContainer now fills its parent (style height "100%"), so the parent's
Tailwind responsive height controls everything.
